request.description:
**Check if user has completed onboarding**

Returns:
```json
{
  "completed": true,
  "onboarding": {
    "preferredGenres": "1,2,3",
    "readingFrequency": "DAILY",
    ...
  }
}
```

**Requires:** Authentication

